data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home in the desirable Carolina Plantations neighborhood. With a split floorplan, an open concept layout, a fenced-in yard, and a convenient two-car garage, this residence offers a delightful blend of style and functionality.The split floorplan of this home ensures privacy and comfort for all. The master suite is a tranquil retreat, complete with its own ensuite bathroom and  walk-in closet, offering a peaceful sanctuary away from the hustle and bustle of the living areas.The open concept layout seamlessly connects the main living spaces, including the living room, dining area, and kitchen. This design promotes a sense of togetherness, making it ideal for both daily living and entertaining. The spacious living room, bathed in natural light, becomes the heart of the home, providing a warm and welcoming atmosphere for relaxation and socializing.Outside, a fenced-in yard offers a secure and private space for outdoor activities.. Enjoy having the luxury of this corner lot. The two-car garage provides not only space for your vehicles but also extra storage and convenience.This ranch-style home represents a harmonious blend of comfort and practicality. Whether you're looking for a welcoming family residence or a place to enjoy your well-deserved retirement, this property offers a little something for everyone. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home sweet home. Schedule a showing today and experience the delightful living this property offers.
